              Email: <a href="mailto:info@flexen.co" class="text-flexen-accent hover:underline">info@flexen.co</a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h3 mb-4 font-bold text-white">2. Scope and Subject Matter</h3>
            <p>
              This website serves general information about Flexen UG and its products only.
              <strong class="text-white">No contracts are concluded</strong> through this website, no goods or services are
              sold and no user accounts are created.
            </p>
