            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              Should individual provisions of these Terms be or become invalid, the validity of the remaining provisions
              shall remain unaffected.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 mt-16 mb-4 font-bold text-white">
            Part B &mdash; Terms of Use for the Flexen App
          </h2>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h3 mb-4 font-bold text-white">&sect; 1 Scope and Contracting Party</h3>
            <p>
