              Use of the app requires a user account. You can register with an email address and password, via Google
              Sign-In or with a phone number.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              You agree to provide truthful and up-to-date information during registration and in your profile. Use of
              the app requires a
              <strong class="text-white">minimum age of 16 years</strong>.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              Keep your login credentials confidential and do not share them with third parties. You are responsible for
