            <p>
              Certain features of the app are only available with a paid subscription or one-time purchase. Currently
              offered:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
              <li><strong class="text-white">Monthly subscription</strong> (base price USD 4.99 per month)</li>
              <li>
                <strong class="text-white">Yearly subscription</strong> (base price USD 47.99 per year) with a 7-day free
