            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              We are neither willing nor obliged to participate in dispute resolution proceedings before a consumer
              arbitration board (Sec. 36 German Consumer Dispute Resolution Act, VSBG).
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
